review_blob: This is one of the worst beers Ive ever had. The price is the only thing enticing. Has a horrid after taste and a tinny initial flavor. Pours out with a decent enough look, but smells like hell. Treat yourself and spend an extra couple of bucks on something that is drinkable.
One of my favorite pints and my favorite brewer. A little light for my taste but this ale pairs extremely well with a fine steak or a lowly burger. Great fruity taste and has great drinkability.
